Police are questioning two people in connection with the murder of 5 women in Mthwalume in KwaZulu-Natal. #eNCA reporter Dasen Thathiah is following the storyt. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Police are questioning two men in connection with the Mthwalume murders. Police have released no further information. READ: Fifth body found in Mthwalume Five bodies have been found in the area in the past five months. Two of the bodies were discovered this week. This is a developing story. We'll update it as and when new information is available.